text: Svetlana Aleksandrovna Kuznetsova (Cyrillic: ; born 27 June 1985) is a Russian professional tennis player who is currently ranked World No. 4. She won the US Open singles title in 2004 and was the runner-up in singles at the French Open in 2006 and the US Open in 2007, losing both finals to Justine Henin in straight sets.
